nodes.text: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness 3, also titled with the legacy numbering Republic 103, is the third issue of the Legends comic book miniseries Star Wars: Dark Times—Out of the Wilderness. It was written by Randy Stradley, illustrated by Douglas Wheatley and Dan Jackson, and first published by Dark Horse Comics on November 30, 2011.
Caged fury! Desert raiders have captured Ember Chankeli, only to discover they have a tiger who can't be tamed! Worse for them: they have a Jedi on their trail!
But Jedi Master Dass Jennir had better watch his back, because a mysterious assassin and Darth Vader both want his head!
